java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.ScrollPaneConstants
public class JTimeBar
extends javax.swing.JScrollPane

This class is used to manage timeline.
We extends it from JScrollPane because JTimeBar should be a JComponent, to simplify coding we used a JScrollPane instead of JComponent. The JTimeBar is built with a JScrollPane, the JScrollPane Store: The JTable or the JList Depends of the ask TimeLine Type.

Author:
laurent Barbisan
